  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>Last updated: August 22, 2025</p>

  <p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how Ghost-Poster handles information.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>OAuth tokens from TikTok to allow video uploading and publishing.</li>
    <li>Basic metadata about videos (e.g., captions, duration).</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>
  <p>We use this information solely to post videos to your TikTok account as requested by you. We do not sell, share, or use your data for any other purpose.</p>

  <h2>3. Data Storage</h2>
  <p>Tokens and data are stored locally on your device. We do not store your data on external servers.</p>

  <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>This app interacts with TikTok’s API. Please review TikTok’s Privacy Policy for their data practices.</p>

  <h2>5. Your Consent</h2>
  <p>By using Ghost-Poster, you consent to this Privacy Policy.</p>

  <h2>6. Changes</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Continued use of the app means acceptance of any changes.</p>

  <p>If you have questions, please contact us at: ghost-poster@example.com</p>
